TO ACTUALLY RUN
sudo go run main.go


Go to https://www.kaihag.com/https-and-go/ to get tutorial on setting up
a simple sel signed open ssl cert and starting the tls server using
http.ListenAndServeTLS

To generate an ssl certificate, either run generate_cert/generate_cert.go
or directly generate an ssl certificate using openssl and follow it's steps:
openssl req -x509 -nodes -days 365 -newkey rsa:2048 -keyout key.pem -out cert.pem
